## Important Notice: Public ≠ Truth-certified (公開 = 真実認定ではない)

**Codex Round 2 採用 最重要警告**:

The visualization, badges, graphs, and ontology in this dataset can produce
an **authority illusion** — making editorial interpretation appear to be
"official position", "shrine-endorsed", or "academic consensus".

**This dataset is editorial interpretation, not certified historical truth.**

Each entry carries:

- `hypothesis_layer` (L0-L5) — strength of the hypothesis
- `confidence_level` (A-E) — historicity assessment
- `verified_status` (verified / under_review / unverified /
  known_fabrication) — existence verification (DISC-006 採択)
- `inference_type` (source_backed / inferential / speculative / symbolic) —
  inferential nature (DISC-005 採択)

**Downstream reusers**: please preserve these epistemic fields when
republishing. Stripping them creates false certainty.

